<%= helpers.model_instructions(
    "Use the Task tool with subagent_type 'apply-feedback' to apply code review feedback from the most recent review.

The apply-feedback agent will:
1. Read the latest review feedback from .aircana/reviews/latest.md
2. Parse and categorize feedback items by severity
3. Confirm changes with you before proceeding
4. Apply fixes in order: Critical, Important, Suggestions
5. Run tests if available to verify changes
6. Provide summary of all changes made

IMPORTANT: The agent will ask for your confirmation before making changes. You can choose to exclude specific items or skip suggestions entirely."
) %>
